<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٥٧٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6785">أَبُو عَوَانَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4042">عَبْدِ الْمَلِكِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3612">عَبْدِ اللهِ بْنِ الْحَارِثِ بْنِ نَوْفَلٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3138">الْعَبَّاسِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ قَالَ لِلنَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: هَلْ نَفَعْتَ أَبَا طَالِبٍ بِشَيْءٍ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>